description: Abundance estimates will be calculated from hydroacoustic and trawl data for each age-class of kokanee.  Production will be calculated by estimating the weight of all kokanee that produced between 2018 and 2019.   Mortality rates of kokanee will be calculated based on the mid-water trawling estimates by dividing this years population estimate by the population estimate for that same cohort last year.  Spawner count data will be compared to previous years.  Kokanee growth rates, maturity, and origin (wild  vs. hatchery) will all be analyzed to assess changes to the kokanee population.  All results will be compared to data from previous years.
title: LPO and DWOR Analysis Status and Trend of Kokanee
